headline.main: Families Aim to Raise $15 Million to Search for Flight 370
headline.print_headline: Families Aim to Raise $15 Million to Search for Flight 370

lead_paragraph: Drones fired missiles at suspected al Qaeda targets in two separate attacks in Yemen on Saturday, local sources said, in what appeared to be a third successive day of U.S. strikes against militants in the Arab country.
